{
  "name": "RPlog_35_ISY_Competition_Chance_vs_Slush",
  "title": "35 ISY Competition: Chance vs. Slush",
  "summary": "In a 35 ISY simulator dueling competition, Flight Officer Liza Molokai (\"Slush\") squares off for the first time against Wing Commander Dante (\"Chance\") in a friendly one-on-one starfighter match. Liza opens by goading her superior over the comm as the two launch, and the duel settles into a long exchange of gunnery and evasive piloting tracked by skill rolls and dropping shield readouts. Liza takes early hits but lands several of her own on Dante, trading warning klaxons and red cockpit glow as both fighters absorb damage. The banter stays light despite the intensity, with Dante chuckling at Molokai's comments and Liza scrambling for clever maneuvers. In the end Dante prevails, bringing her fighter to rest alongside Liza's as the stunned but gracious cadet offers her congratulations.",
